name: Soup Prayer
description:
A spoken word, media-rich poem by Ana Maria Caballero.

Caballero's writing has won the Beverly International Prize for Literature, Colombia's José Miguel Arango National Poetry Prize + been a finalist for the Academy of American Poets Prize.

Her NFTs are available via KnownOrigin, Fort Gallery NFT, MONOGRAMA NFT Gallery, Async.Art, Foundation, Etherpoems, HEN + will be displayed at Dreamverse during NFT.NYC 2021.
